WebSocketFuzzMessagesViewModel
public class WebSocketMessagesViewModel
extends PagingTableModel<WebSocketMessageDTO>

This model uses the TableWebSocket instance to load only needed entries from database. Moreover it shows only those entries that are not blacklisted by given WebSocketMessagesViewFilter.
